
<h1 class="govuk-heading-l datagovuk-heading-l">English Housing Survey</h1>

<section class="govuk-section datagovuk-section">
  <p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">A collection of detailed time series data tables on people’s housing circumstances and the condition and energy efficiency of the English housing stock. The data is updated each year and includes: </p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet datagovuk-list">
  <li>parking, mains gas and EV charge points</li>
<li>dwelling condition, safety and security</li>
<li>energy performance, heating and insulation</li>
<li>leaseholders </li>
<li>new households and recent movers</li>
<li>owner occupiers, recent first-time buyers and second homes</li>
<li>social and private renters</li>
<li>stock profile</li>
<li>tenure trends and cross tenure analysis </li>

</ul>
<p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">These datasets are owned by the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government.</p>
</section>


